question_id: Siapa pelanggan yang paling sering menyewa film? Sertakan nama depan, nama belakang, dan jumlah sewanya.
sql_query:
SELECT
    c.first_name AS nama_depan,
    c.last_name AS nama_belakang,
    COUNT(r.rental_id) AS jumlah_sewa
FROM
    customer c
JOIN
    rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id
JOIN
    film f ON r.rental_id = f.film_id
GROUP BY
    c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name
ORDER BY
    jumlah_sewa DESC
raw_response:
